QuestData.Title: A Different Outcome
QuestData.Description:
There is no way to know when these orders were sent, or received.
Rokor took some Seekers north some time ago. They must be in that region by now.
If the temple still stands, warn Gral and his followers.
If it is lost, we must do what we can.
QuestData.LogDescription: Find Rokor near Atal'Gral, to the north.
